in his vision,and guess what?

01:23.850 --> 01:25.670
A plane crashed.How is this different?

01:25.680 --> 01:27.900
You mean apart from the
ethereal woman dressed in white?

01:27.910 --> 01:29.960
Which sounds an awful
lot like the virgin mary,

01:29.970 --> 01:35.900
