of impending disaster like,say,a plane crash.

01:35.910 --> 01:37.730
I googled "disaster" and "women.

01:37.740 --> 01:40.060
" Had to wade through hundreds of
sites of sarah palin and britney spears.

01:40.070 --> 01:42.260
Replaced by technology.Well,it
wouldn't be the first.

