How do I prevent a plane crash?

01:43.920 --> 01:46.950
Well,it would help to know
whatlight it was,or the airline.

01:46.960 --> 01:50.350
You don't even know
what field it crashed in.

01:50.360 --> 01:52.890
And you really want to know why I'm
cheating on you with the internet?

01:52.900 --> 01:57.130
All right,fine.Why don't you go back online
and see what you can learn about this woman?

01:57.140 --> 01:59.930
They're so tiny and adorable.

01:59.940 --> 02:01.180
Daddy,where did you get these?

02:01.190 --> 02:02.590
They were yours.

02:02.600 --> 02:04.620
To be honest,I considered
throwing them away,

02:04.630 --> 02:07.040
but your mother wouldn't let me.

02:07.050 --> 02:13.580
They were her baby shoes and her
mother's,and now they're yours again.

02:14.610 --> 02:16.740
Me and matt.

02:16.750 --> 02:19.440
Who would've thought,right?

02:19.450 --> 02:21.010
The two of you...

02:21.020 --> 02:23.100
you're happy?

02:23.110 --> 02:24.630
We are.

02:24.640 --> 02:27.100
You know,I thought working together
again was gonna drive me nuts,

02:27.110 --> 02:32.930
but after seeing his little frat boy face all day long,can you
believe I actually really look forward to seeing it again at night?

02:32.940 --> 02:34.480
He's a lucky man.

02:34.490 --> 02:37.200
The truth is,I think I'm the lucky one.

02:37.210 --> 02:42.350
You know me.I'm always waiting
for the other shoe to drop.But...

02:42.360 --> 02:44.080
I don't know.

02:44.090 --> 02:48.100
This time,I don't think it's going to.

02:49.310 --> 02:51.910
Are you okay?

02:51.920 --> 02:55.120
I've been thinking about
your mother a lot lately.

02:55.130 --> 02:58.380
Believe it or not,I actually called her.

02:58.390 --> 03:01.130
You what?Way to bury the lead.

03:01.140 --> 03:02.990
- What did she say?
- Nothing.

03:03.000 --> 03:08.130
