someone calling repeatedly and then hanging up.

03:08.140 --> 03:08.870
DaD.

03:08.880 --> 03:10.940
The phone ringing always
seemed to be the interval

03:10.950 --> 03:16.130
where in my mind a genuine attempt at
reconciliation became a fool's errand.

03:16.140 --> 03:19.420
Maybe if you'd given her
the chance to answer...

03:19.430 --> 03:21.220
maybe you'd be surprised.

03:21.230 --> 03:25.570
That has been happening with more
and more frequency as I get older--

03:25.580 --> 03:29.420
eli,you,matt.

03:32.850 --> 03:38.790
When you talk to mom,tell
her I said thanks for these.

03:38.800 --> 03:41.110
tammy,can you get
these redlined by noon?

03:41.120 --> 03:44.350
Also aaron in research needs
the list of housing N.P.O.S,

03:44.360 --> 03:46.820
and I'm gonna need you to revise the
citations for the salma-hoyt brief.

03:46.830 --> 03:50.650
The blue book on them's a disaster.

03:52.520 --> 03:57.050
